title: Sample Book, The American Court Collection - The Beige Collection, Volume D, 1959
title_raw: The American Court Collection - The Beige Collection, Volume D
medium: screen-printed and mezzotone print on paper
description: Book includes 31 patterns with multiple colorways of most patterns. Includes Central Park and Chicken Wire by Ilonka Karasz, Etruscan, Lanterns, Chinese Peony, Fancy Fruits and Vegetables by Marion Dorn, Baiae and Cathedral by Paul Johnson, White Birches by Lanette, and Midnight Supper by Peter Mitchell. Also includes a black and white photo insert of Stairs by Ilonka karasz. Also included is House & Garden Cook Book Wallpaper printed in the blueprint process.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book, The American Court Collection - The Beige Collection, Volume D, 1959; Designed by Lanette Scheeline, Ilonka Karasz, Oscar Berger, Marion Dorn Kauffer, William Justema and Peter Todd Mitchell; USA; screen-printed and mezzotone print on paper; 52 x 37 cm (20 1/2 x 14 9/16 in.); 1980-77-6-1/65
